```

## 4. Meilisearch v1.10

- Host: `http://localhost:7700`
- Master key: `${MEILI_MASTER_KEY}`
- Mode: `${MEILI_ENV}` (Authorization header required)

```bash
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer ${MEILI_MASTER_KEY}" http://localhost:7700/health
```

