## 6. Local mode caveats

- Services bind to `0.0.0.0` on the host. If you only want loopback, edit
  `core/compose/docker-compose.yml` and change `0.0.0.0:<port>` to
  `127.0.0.1:<port>`.
- No public ingress. To expose services on a domain, switch to `full` mode.
- No CI/CD. Apps run wherever you choose to run them — outside this stack.
